    },
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "Let's meet #b#p226##k the Security Guy at the #m10001100#."
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "At the dungeon entrance, I met #p226#, the guard. He said he wanted to make a nourishing meal for his mother and asked me to hunt #r20 #o18#s#k and #r20 #o17#s#k, then bring back #b10 #t4000018#s#k, #b10 #t4000017#s#k, and #b1 #t2020000##k. He said he’s too busy with his guard duties... but honestly, he just looks like he’s about to fall asleep...?!"
    },
    "2": {
      "_dirName": "2",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "I got #p226#, who is protecting the entrance of the Dungeon, the stuff he asked for. Since he's making the \"Snake Drink\" and all... I want a taste of that myself! In return, #p226# gave me a nicely refined jewel he found from around the area. It's not like refined jewels fall from the sky... did someone lose it while traveling? Anyway, I should drop by later when the \"Snake Drink\" is ready..."
    },
    "demandSummary": {
      "_dirName": "demandSummary",
      "_dirType": "String",
      "_value": "#o18# #a101131#\\n#o17# #a101132#\\n#i4000018# #t4000018# #b#c4000018##k / 10\\n#i4000017# #t4000017# #b#c4000017##k / 10\\n#i2020000# #t2020000# #b#c2020000##k / 1"
    }
