  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hmmm... wait! You must be pretty strong, huh? I have a favor to ask you... as a good son, every year I make my mom a special, healthy, and tasty dish, but I don't have any free time these days from all this guarding. I'm sorry, but can you help me get the ingredients needed for the dish?"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Alright! This year I'm trying to make my mom a very tasty Snake Drink! Can you hunt some monsters and bring me #b10 #t4000018#s#k, #b10 #t4000017#s#k, and, for dessert, #b1 #t2020000##k please? Please find me once you have gathered them all up!"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Must be busy here and there, huh? Please come back and do me a favor when you have some spare time."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh my... you actually gathered them all up!! This will definitely help me make a very tasty Snake Drink... it's a very rare drink so I wouldn't be sharing this with anyone else, but I'll make an exception for you... so when the drink is done, please drop by and have some with us. Promise?"
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh yeah... since you worked hard to get me all the ingredients, I need to give you something in return. Now, what would be good... Oh yeah! Around here you'll see lots of shiny, sparkling objects. I've been collecting a lot of them, but as of this moment, they're yours. This will help you through your journey. Here, take it."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Got it? Thanks for your help... Now I must rush back home! So long~"
        }
      },
